  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要为这个项目画一个甘特图，时间范围是2014年初。整体标题就叫\"A Gantt Diagram\"吧。另外，数据格式要用YYYY-MM-DD这种标准格式。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "title",
        "dateFormat"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "好的，标题设为\"A Gantt Diagram\"，日期格式用YYYY-MM-DD。那任务怎么划分板块？需要几个section？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "title",
        "dateFormat",
        "section"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "分两个板块。第一个叫\"Section\"，里面放两个任务：第一个任务叫\"A task\"，从2014年1月1号开始，持续30天，标记为a1；第二个叫\"Another task\"，要接在a1后面，持续20天。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "section",
        "A task",
        "a1",
        "Another task",
        "after a1"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "明白了，第一个section加好了。A task从2014-01-01开始30天，标记a1；Another task用after a1衔接，20天。第二个section怎么安排？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Section",
        "A task",
        "Another task",
        "a1"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "第二个section叫\"Another\"。里面第一个任务叫\"Task in sec\"，从1月12号开始，持续12天。还有一个\"another task\"，这个比较特殊——它不需要指定开始日期，只给24天的工期，让它自动排就行。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Another",
        "Task in sec",
        "another task"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "确认一下：\"another task\"只写24d，不指定开始日期，系统会自动计算对吧？还有，这个任务名称我注意到你用的是小写开头，和前面的\"Another task\"大小写有点区别，需要统一吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "another task",
        "24d"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，\"another task\"就保持小写开头，和前面的\"Another task\"区分开，这样没问题。不指定开始日期，自动排程。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "another task"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "全部完成了。两个section，四个任务，日期格式和依赖关系都按你说的设置好了。你看看还有要调整的吗？",
